Definition: dissociative disorder in which a person forgets who they are and leaves home to create a new life
Example: during the fugue there is no memory of the former life; after recovering there is no memory for events during the dissociative state
Synonyms: psychogenic_fugue, dissociative_disorder, dissociative, disorder, in, which, a, person, forgets, who, they, are, and, leaves, home, to, create, new, life, during, the, there, is, no, memory, of, former, after, recovering, for, events, state
Category: noun.state
